@Weak

The song choice didn't seem random to me.  One word will often trigger a song in my head.  

When the Wordplay column mentions a song, it's usually something very obvious and very well known, and frankly, a little boring.  In Crossword Fiend, the connections are sometimes tenuous and the choices are more interesting, at least to me.  I'm more likely to learn about a song, which I always like.

